ETHICAL USE STATEMENT

This toolkit is intended for defensive security research, investigative
journalism, corporate due diligence, bug bounty work in scope, and
educational purposes. It collects only information that is publicly
available through passive OSINT sources.

Users are responsible for complying with all applicable laws and terms of
service. Do not use this toolkit to harass individuals, stalk, dox, or
otherwise cause harm. OSINT is a tool. Use it to protect, not to attack.
